{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./ImportGraph/Imports/RequiredModules.html#Lean.Environment.requiredModules\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Environment</span>.<span class=\"name\">requiredModules</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">env</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Environment.html#Lean.Environment\">Environment</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Data/NameMap/Basic.html#Lean.NameSet\">NameSet</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Return the names of the modules in which constants used in the current file were defined.\n\nNote that this will *not* account for tactics and syntax used in the file,\nso the results may not suffice as imports.\n","docLink":"./ImportGraph/Imports/RequiredModules.html#Lean.Environment.requiredModules","kind":"def","line":145,"name":"Lean.Environment.requiredModules","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/import-graph/blob/85b59af46828c029a9168f2f9c35119bd0721e6e/ImportGraph/Imports/RequiredModules.lean#L145-L161"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./ImportGraph/Imports/RequiredModules.html#Lean.Environment.transitivelyRequiredModules'\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Environment</span>.<span class=\"name\">transitivelyRequiredModules'</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">env</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Environment.html#Lean.Environment\">Environment</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">modules</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<spa